OL,3,CFire boss resignation accepted after
OL,4,Cattempted withdrawal
OL,6,FIn a dramatic turn of events, Oliver
OL,7,FLee, the suspended interim Chief
OL,8,FExecutive of West Midlands Fire
OL,9,FService (WMFS), has had his
OL,10,Fresignation accepted, following days
OL,11,Fof leadership turmoil and escalating
OL,12,Ftensions over the service's governance.
OL,14,FLee, who initially resigned last week
OL,15,Fafter being suspended, reversed his
OL,16,Fdecision on Monday, citing hopes that
OL,17,Fthe situation had improved after the
OL,18,Fresignation of the Fire Authority
OL,19,Fchair, Greg Brackenridge.
