OL,3,CFire boss resignation accepted after
OL,4,Cattempted withdrawal
OL,6,F"I felt over the weekend that the
OL,7,Fsituation might have changed in the
OL,8,Fface of the Chair's resignation.
OL,10,F"So, for 1,900 people, I made my first
OL,11,Fever U-turn, and withdrew my
OL,12,Fresignation. To help," Lee explained.
OL,14,FHowever, on Monday, the West Midlands
OL,15,FFire Authority (WMFRA) confirmed
OL,16,Fduring a full meeting at WMFS
OL,17,FHeadquarters that Lee's resignation
OL,18,Fhad been formally accepted,
OL,19,Fterminating his employment with
OL,20,Fimmediate effect.
