OL,6,FShe added that Deputy Chief Fire
OL,7,FOfficer Simon Barry will continue to
OL,8,Flead the service until a permanent
OL,9,FChief Fire Officer/Chief Executive is
OL,10,Fappointed.
OL,12,FMiks expressed her appreciation for
OL,13,FWMFS staff during this challenging
OL,14,Ftime, emphasising the Authority's
OL,15,Fcommitment to supporting them as they
OL,16,Fprovide essential services to the West
OL,17,FMidlands community.
