OL,6,FThe leadership crisis, which has been
OL,7,Funfolding since Lee's suspension,
OL,8,Fstems from his outspoken criticism of
OL,9,FWMFS's governance.
OL,11,FLee had described the governance
OL,12,Fstructure as "wholly impossible" with
OL,13,Felements of dishonesty within the
OL,14,Forganisation.
OL,16,FFire Authority chair Cllr
OL,17,FBrackenridge, who resigned on
OL,18,FSaturday, called recent events "an
OL,19,Funnecessary distraction."
